T02D3064:119b-1: shukla tsanda ma h'a ro sha na s'a dha nam /
T02D3064:119b-3: gtum po dkar po chen po'i sgrub thabs /
T02D3064:119b-4: gtum po khro bo chen po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D3064:119b-5: sngags pas re zhig thog mar stong pa nyid bsgoms te /
T02D3064:119b-6: de'i ngang las sna tshogs padma dang nyi ma'i steng
T02D3064:119b-7: du zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa sku mdog dkar po
T02D3064:120a-1: rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan pa /
T02D3064:120a-2: rin po che'i cod pan can /
T02D3064:120a-3: phyag g-yas pa ral gri spyi bor 'phyar ba /
T02D3064:120a-4: g-yon pa sdigs mdzub dang bcas pa'i zhags pa snying gar 'dzin pa /
T02D3064:120a-5: zhabs g-yas pa tsog pur bzhugs shing /
T02D3064:120a-6: g-yon pa'i pus mo nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la rab tu btsugs pa /
T02D3064:120a-7: lha'i na bza' gos su gyon pa /
T02D3064:120a-8: snying gar sna tshogs padma dang nyi ma'i dbus su
T02D3064:120a-9: yi ge h'um la yi ge dgus bskor ba dang
T02D3064:120a-10: bcas pa'i bcom ldan 'das bsgom par bya'o //
T02D3064:120a-11: de'i mdun du de dang kha sbyor zhing yang de
T02D3064:120a-12: kho na dang 'dra ba'i bcom ldan 'das gnyis pa
T02D3064:120a-13: bsgom bar bya'o // de'i rjes su rang gi snying
T02D3064:120a-14: ga'i sngags las 'phros pa'i sngags kyi phreng ba rang
T02D3064:120a-15: gi kha nas mdun gyi bcom ldan 'das kyi zhal
T02D3064:120a-16: du zhugs shing de'i lte ba nas rang gi lte
T02D3064:120a-17: bar zhugs shing yang rang gi snying gar 'thon nas
T02D3064:120a-18: de kho na bzhin 'khor bar bsgom par bya'o //
T02D3064:120a-19: bzlas pa'i tshe rang gi snying ga'i h'um gi 'od
T02D3064:120a-20: zer gyis sangs rgyas dang byang chub sems dpa'i ye
T02D3064:120a-25: sgyu rtsal drug cu rtsa bzhi'i nus pa dang /
T02D3064:120a-26: rig pa la sogs pa la mkhas pa'i yon tan dang /
T02D3064:120a-27: gzhan zil gyis gnon pa'i rtsod pa dang /
T02D3064:120a-28: snyan ngag la sogs pa'i yon tan ma lus pa
T02D3064:120a-29: bkug nas rang gi snying ga'i h'um la rab tu
T02D3064:120a-30: thim zhing / bdag nyid rig pa lnga la mkhas
T02D3064:120a-31: pa'i pandi ta yin no snyam pa'i nga rgyal dang
T02D3064:120a-32: ldan pa'i spobs pas sngags bzlas par bya'o //
T02D3064:120a-33: zhag nyi shu rtsa gcig bzlas pas snyan ngag mkhan chen por 'gyur ro //
T02D3064:120a-34: gtum po khro bo chen po'i shes rab blo 'phel gyi sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
